<author>Iliyas Tursun</author>
<title>Erkin, erkin, men erkin ҲС89</title>
<key>Am</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Am
 Erkin, erkin, men erkin
.Dm                  Am
 Shaytonning qulligidan
.E
 Berilgan men uchun qurbonlik
.                    Am
 Erkin, erkin, men erkin

[C1]
.     Dm
   // Xalos, xalos boʻlganman
.  Am
   Qullikdan men qutulganman
.  E
   Men uchun Tangri toʻkdi qonin //
.                     Am
   Erkin, erkin, men erkin

[V2]
 Erkin, erkin, men erkin
 Gunohning zanjiridan
 Rab Isoning qoni bilan
 Erkin, erkin, men erkin</lyrics>
</song>